        android:layout_marginStart="16dp"
        android:layout_marginTop="24dp"
        android:text="When you have the privilege and responsibility of leading a company, having the right skill set is vital to success. Business owners and managers need to understand the difference between a leader and a boss and which skills distinguish the two. Below is a personally curated, tried-and-tested list of the 5 most important leadership skills needed to succeed in business."
